ActCanadian Commercial Corporation Act
PrecisAppointment of CHARLES PAUL MARCOTTE of Ottawa, Ontario, to be President of the Canadian Commercial Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, or until such time as a new President is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective December 16, 2019.
